CEPA 5 200607194



In last summer, I spend my holiday with my friends. It was the best holiday in my life. We traveled to Malisya by plane. We arrived their after along journey. First, we took rest in the hotel. In the next day we visited the park, the weather was very nice and the people were friendly. We had a walk then we dicided to play the Games, It was fear Games but we enjoyed it. Then we went to shopping malls to buy something to our families. It was very big and their was nice things to buy, everyone from us buy presents for her family. The third day we went to the twin towers they were very tall and big, we reached to the top fastly, and we took some photos from their. It was amazing place to visit. Then our friends Mona want to go to cooler place by “Telefreec”, All of uwe went with her, it was a very green area in the mountain, so we also took photo their. after two weeks we back home to UAE. It was the best holiday ever, because I went with my best friends to the best country in my boint of view.

I spent a wonderful holiday in Eygpt . I am and my family went to the Airport at 10:00 Am. We  arrived to Cairo Airport at 2:00 pm . Firstly we went to the hotel to take arest and to eat. Then,  we went out to the park to enjoy a nature. My father decide to take us to the Nile river in the evening. In the evening , we reached there and we took a boat to sail in the Nile. It was very  wonderful place that I visited in my life .
We ate our dinner in the boat. Our meal is consist of meat, salad, chicken and many Eygption foods.
After we finished our sailing in the Nile. We went back to the hotel ( In the next day , my father was prepare us a very big surprise . It was a visit to pyramids. We were very interesting in that place.
I take my camera to take a photographes for us. We walked around this place for long time. In the next day, we went back to the UAE. Really I had a wonderful vacation in Eygpt that I will not forget it easily.

                                		Summer holiday 


Last summer holiday was my best holiday. I had a great time with my family. We went to Malisya and stayed there for two weeks. The weather was funtastic.
We visited The museume and saw the old things That they used , It was interesting for all of us.
In one beautful morning we went to the most beautiful park I have ever seen, there we had a great time 
we played and had our lunch .
In the next day we went sailling in the boat we enjoyed on the view of the blue see and the green vast area.
I learned how to catch fish, My father and my two brothers swam in the see,  I wanted to swim too bot I was abit scared .
We visited many cities and learned different cultural. really it was the best summer holiday I had .
